---
import Layout from "~/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Section from "~/components/Section.astro";
import Container from "~/components/Container.astro";
import GridAlt from "~/components/GridAlt.astro";
import Heading from "~/components/Heading.astro";
import Article from "~/components/Article.astro";
import CardGridAlt from "~/components/CardGridAlt.astro";
---

<Layout pageTitle="Services">
  <Section>
    <Container>
      <Heading>
        <h2 slot="heading-title">Our Premium Travel Services</h2>

        <p slot="heading-content">
          Experience Colombia like never before with our specialized travel
          services. From expertly guided tours to reliable transportation
          solutions, we're committed to making your Colombian adventure
          unforgettable.
        </p>
      </Heading>
      <GridAlt>
        <CardGridAlt
          title="Guided Tours"
          description="Discover Colombia's hidden gems with our expert local guides. From cultural heritage sites to breathtaking natural wonders, our carefully crafted tours provide authentic and immersive experiences."
          color="brand"
          icon="map"
          href="/services/tours"
        />
        <CardGridAlt
          title="Transportation"
          description="Travel with confidence throughout Colombia with our reliable transportation services. From airport transfers to private vehicles, we ensure safe, comfortable, and efficient travel options."
          color="brand"
          icon="car"
          href="/services/transportation"
        />
      </GridAlt>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <Section>
    <Container>
      <Article>
        <h2>Our Specialized Travel Services</h2>
        <p>
          At Get Inside Colombia, we focus on providing exceptional travel
          experiences through our two core services: guided tours and reliable
          transportation. Our team of experienced professionals is dedicated to
          ensuring your Colombian adventure is seamless, authentic, and
          unforgettable from start to finish.
        </p>
        <h3>Guided Tours</h3>
        <p>
          Our expert-led tours showcase the very best of Colombia's diverse
          landscapes, rich culture, and vibrant history. Each tour is
          thoughtfully designed to provide authentic experiences while ensuring
          your comfort and safety throughout your journey.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Cultural heritage tours</li>
          <li>Adventure and nature expeditions</li>
          <li>City exploration experiences</li>
          <li>Culinary and coffee tours</li>
        </ul>
        <blockquote>
          "Discover the real Colombia with guides who know it best."
        </blockquote>
        <p>
          Whether you're interested in exploring colonial cities, hiking through
          lush landscapes, or immersing yourself in local traditions, our
          professional guides bring each destination to life with their in-depth
          knowledge and passion for sharing Colombian culture.
        </p>
        <h3>Transportation Services</h3>
        <p>
          Navigate Colombia with ease using our reliable transportation
          solutions. We understand that comfortable, safe travel is essential to
          enjoying your Colombian experience, which is why we offer a range of
          transportation options to meet your specific needs.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Airport transfers</li>
          <li>Private vehicles with drivers</li>
          <li>Inter-city transportation</li>
          <li>Custom transportation packages</li>
        </ul>
        <blockquote>
          "Safe, reliable transportation throughout your Colombian journey."
        </blockquote>
        <p>
          Our fleet of well-maintained vehicles and professional drivers ensure
          you reach your destinations safely and comfortably. Whether you need a
          simple airport pickup or comprehensive transportation for your entire
          Colombian adventure, we provide seamless service that allows you to
          focus on enjoying your experience.
        </p>
        <h3>Why Choose Our Services</h3>
        <p>
          When you choose Get Inside Colombia, you're selecting a team that
          prioritizes:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Authentic local experiences</li>
          <li>Safety and reliability</li>
          <li>Personalized attention</li>
          <li>Sustainable tourism practices</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Our services are designed to complement each other perfectly, allowing
          you to create a comprehensive Colombian experience tailored to your
          interests and preferences. Whether you book a single day tour or plan
          an extensive journey throughout the country, our team is committed to
          exceeding your expectations at every step.
        </p>
        <p>
          Contact us today to discuss how our guided tours and transportation
          services can help you discover the magic of Colombia in comfort and
          style. Our travel specialists are ready to help you plan the perfect
          Colombian adventure.
        </p>
      </Article>
    </Container>
  </Section>
</Layout>
